fits of dogs in the office', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'working-like-a-dog-benefits-of-dogs-in-the-office-2', '', '', '2018-04-09 12:14:01', '2018-04-09 12:14:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/MADS-foodog/wordpress/?p=59', 0, 'post', '', 0),
